text: Edona Kastrati (born 12 August 1999) is an Italian–Kosovan footballer who plays as a defender for Serie B club Lady Granata Cittadella and the Kosovo women's national team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Italian women's footballers Category:Italian people of Kosovan descent
